Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.33,0:01:53.37,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What are you saying?\NWhat's wrong, Norman?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:54.25,0:01:56.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You already know by now, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.50,0:02:00.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I set a trap for three people.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.84,0:02:04.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Don, I said the rope was under my bed.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.51,0:02:07.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,To Gilda, I said\Nthe second floor bathroom's ceiling.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.93,0:02:10.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's what I told you, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.72,0:02:15.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But actually, I told Don it was in the dining hall,\Nand told Gilda it was in the library.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.90,0:02:19.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, the rope\Nthat was under my bed disappeared.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.28,0:02:22.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then what about the other two locations?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.11,0:02:25.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Should we go check on them now?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.05,0:02:48.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Dang. And I thought I was doing so well.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.81,0:02:55.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.02,0:02:57.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I am Mom's spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.19,0:03:01.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,When did you start suspecting me?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:02.57,0:03:04.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The day Sister came to the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.57,0:03:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was disgusted with myself\Nfor thinking such a thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:08.91,0:03:11.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were the first person I suspected.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.37,0:03:13.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even though you're my friend.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.46,0:03:16.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I just wished it wasn't true.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.96,0:03:20.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was my supposition for the worst case.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.05,0:03:24.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But for us, it would be the most problematic\Nif you're the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.84,0:03:28.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And from the enemy's point of view, it would be\Nthe most beneficial if you're the traitor.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:32.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You can give opinions to our plans,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.52,0:03:35.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,and from the perspective of controlling\Nthe situation, it's perfect.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.89,0:03:38.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No one else fit the job better.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.23,0:03:40.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's why you suspected me.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.57,0:03:46.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And that's how I walked into your trap, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.32,0:03:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One more thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.11,0:03:52.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, you're not a traitor\Nwho was set up just for this matter, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.70,0:03:57.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom would never trust a sudden tip\Nor an impromptu spy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.87,0:04:01.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How long have you been Mom's spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.50,0:04:04.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,From a long time ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.38,0:04:07.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been Mom's subordinate for a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.93,0:04:10.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Basically, a sheepdog for a shepherd.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.68,0:04:13.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about everything\Nand assisted Mom this whole time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.89,0:04:14.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.69,0:04:20.48,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was everything a lie?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.48,0:04:24.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,All the time spent\Npreparing for things with Emma and me?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.90,0:04:28.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What and how much did you tell Mom?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.32,0:04:30.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tracking devices can be broken, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.70,0:04:32.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the point in asking that?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:32.74,0:04:34.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Depending on the answer, will you cut me off?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.95,0:04:39.67,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I won't. I'll have you by our side,\Nas you've always been.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.96,0:04:44.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Aren't you glad? You can continue\Nto hide the mistake you made.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.30,0:04:47.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wanted to keep spying on us,\Neven if it meant framing Don, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.34,0:04:49.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What do you want?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.76,0:04:51.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three things.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.18,0:04:57.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, continue to spend time with us like before\Nand guarantee our safety.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.73,0:05:01.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two, release all the information you have to us.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.56,0:05:03.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Three, come to our side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:04.32,0:05:06.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Can you become my spy?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:08.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You want me to be the ace up your sleeve?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.61,0:05:09.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.45,0:05:11.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Are you an idiot?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.07,0:05:14.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If that was your objective from the beginning,\Nyou should've kept quiet and used me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.74,0:05:18.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just forcibly utilize me and then abandon me\Nwhen you execute the plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.41,0:05:20.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That would've been the better method.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.75,0:05:22.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.34,0:05:30.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She said we're family that grew up together.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.01,0:05:39.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I changed my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.48,0:05:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to believe in you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.65,0:05:44.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That you're my friend before my enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.19,0:05:49.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, you're the one\Nwho hid Little Bunny, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.49,0:05:54.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That night when we went to the gate,\Nif you hadn't said that we could make it
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.91,0:05:56.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,we wouldn't have gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.12,0:06:03.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You led us to discover the truth\Nabout this House for ourselves.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're the one who set up\Nthis escape for our sake, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.21,0:06:11.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, why are you being Mom's sheepdog?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.17,0:06:13.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Why?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.43,0:06:18.51,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You wouldn't do things to make us realize the truth\Nif you were 100 percent Mom's dog.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.39,0:06:22.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were controlling us.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:22.81,0:06:28.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tracking devices, the timing of the escape,\Nand how fast the plan progressed.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.52,0:06:31.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why you strongly opposed\Nescaping ten days from now.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:32.36,0:06:36.07,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But at the same time,\Nweren't you also keeping Mom under control?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.66,0:06:39.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not our enemy after all, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.95,0:06:43.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I volunteered. I went to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.33,0:06:48.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, it's more accurate to say\Nthat I sold myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:49.25,0:06:52.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was all in preparation for this escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.38,0:06:59.22,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The most efficient way to learn about the enemy\Nand gather things is from inside their pocket.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.43,0:07:02.64,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I brought up a deal to Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.89,0:07:04.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.23,0:07:05.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I had chances to succeed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.19,0:07:11.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom would want to avoid harvesting a top scorer,\None she spent time and effort on, midway.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.19,0:07:13.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's how I saw it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.28,0:07:17.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She actually cares more\Nabout profit rather than rules.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.70,0:07:19.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I basically asked for two things.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.24,0:07:23.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One, I'll cooperate,\Nso don't immediately ship me out.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.95,0:07:27.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Two, I asked for rewards if I gave results.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.63,0:07:28.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Rewards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.13,0:07:30.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just various junk.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.92,0:07:33.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If it wasn't available in the House,\NI had her obtain it.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.68,0:07:40.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was testing what I could obtain\Nand what was impossible.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.89,0:07:43.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I also wanted to probe the outside world.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:43.47,0:07:48.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,As a result, she obtained a lot of things,\Nas long as they weren't dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:48.06,0:07:50.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But they were all older models.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.32,0:07:55.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then, when you said you had an idea\Nabout breaking the tracking devices...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.36,0:07:57.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've seen the actual device.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.49,0:08:02.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I experimented, and after many years,\NI figured out how to break it.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.12,0:08:05.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tracking devices can definitely be nullified.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.00,0:08:08.04,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you understand?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.46,0:08:12.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The person you see before you\Nis the strongest card you have.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.59,0:08:15.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The tracking devices and Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.63,0:08:21.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have far more information\Nthan what's necessary for this escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.64,0:08:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I've been preparing ever since\NI found out the truth about the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.64,0:08:29.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.77,0:08:34.32,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Without having anyone notice,\NI had you two go to the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.73,0:08:38.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I did all this to make sure\Nyou two don't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.74,0:08:45.41,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Just like you said, I'm not your enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.41,0:08:46.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I'm also not an ally.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.33,0:08:51.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Under one condition,\NI can completely become your ace.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:51.79,0:08:57.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll give you all the information I have,\Nand I'll also leak lies to Mom like you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.51,0:08:58.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What's the condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.72,0:09:00.09,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Trick Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.09,0:09:04.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You need to pretend we're taking everyone,\Nbut at the last moment, ditch them.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.68,0:09:07.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if we take others,\Nit'll only be Don and Gilda.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.43,0:09:10.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're telling me to give up on\Nescaping with everyone?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.56,0:09:11.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:11.65,0:09:14.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The training is helping everyone grow\Nmore than we expected.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.86,0:09:16.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You even said their movement isn't bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.53,0:09:19.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You meant that, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:19.15,0:09:20.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Then we can all—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.15,0:09:22.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It still doesn't change the fact\Nthat they're a burden.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.20,0:09:28.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you were going to help us.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.45,0:09:30.71,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And this is how I'm helping.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:34.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Otherwise, you and Emma can die here.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.63,0:09:38.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I thought you didn't want us to get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.76,0:09:42.43,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If you're just going to get killed as soon as\Nwe escape, it'd be better to get shipped out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.22,0:09:46.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So? Will you accept my condition?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.19,0:09:53.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.57,0:10:01.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,If what you just said was a lie...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:02.74,0:10:05.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I know. It wasn't a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:17.90,0:11:19.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You took a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.82,0:11:21.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I was talking to Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.73,0:11:22.74,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.07,0:11:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Nothing much has changed.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.95,0:11:27.03,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're focused on training with tag.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.62,0:11:29.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The bigger issue is that Sister.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.99,0:11:31.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,She's on the move again.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.74,0:11:33.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.66,0:11:34.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:35.25,0:11:37.88,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You should have never summoned her.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.88,0:11:41.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That was supposed to be\Na deterrent for me, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.17,0:11:46.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It makes me sad that you still don't trust me\Neven though I've been helping you for six years.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.38,0:11:48.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a precaution.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.51,0:11:52.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, if you had made sure those two\Ndidn't go to the gate that day,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.85,0:11:55.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,this wouldn't be happening.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.39,0:11:56.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I apologized for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.85,0:12:02.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I never thought you'd be a useless dog\Nwho couldn't even keep watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.98,0:12:05.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I made up for it by spying for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.28,0:12:10.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I sold out my best friends, and I report\NSister Krone's disturbing behavior in detail.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.62,0:12:12.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I'm going to get my reward.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.04,0:12:15.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Of course. That is the deal.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.17,0:12:25.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,With everyone... Let's escape with everyone!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.21,0:12:26.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And of course, with Ray, too!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.89,0:12:37.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.56,0:12:39.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I told you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:41.73,0:12:42.65,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.78,0:12:45.73,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.78,0:12:48.95,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.54,0:13:02.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Norman, it's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.47,0:13:09.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.81,0:13:16.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- So then I did this...\N- Good morning, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.39,0:13:18.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.02,0:13:20.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Good morning, Norman.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.35,0:13:21.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I brought the plates.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.90,0:13:23.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- Good morning, Ray.\N- Good morning, Emma.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.19,0:13:26.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.40,0:13:28.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How did the plan with the ropes go?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.28,0:13:30.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Was there progress\Nfor the source of information?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.24,0:13:31.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.11,0:13:32.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:32.62,0:13:33.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's me.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.49,0:13:36.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm Mom's informant.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.00,0:13:41.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It was you?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.42,0:13:50.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry for that reaction,\Nbut I still don't understand.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.47,0:13:52.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yes! Let me explain!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.35,0:13:57.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're the traitor, but not an enemy.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:57.89,0:14:01.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You were acting as Mom's subordinate\Nall this time for our sake?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.02,0:14:02.98,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.98,0:14:08.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The truth is, I was going to tell you everything\Nas soon as you got back from the gate.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.57,0:14:11.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But you left Little Bunny behind,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.99,0:14:15.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,saying you wanted to escape with everyone,\Nand other unexpected things happened.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.99,0:14:19.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom found out,\Nso I had to manage the situation.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.79,0:14:22.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Plus you guys were being rash,\Nand about to get reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:22.67,0:14:26.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's why I figured I should keep quiet\Nand get both under control.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.67,0:14:30.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So you're saying that you\Nwere covering up for our mistakes.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.80,0:14:34.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And you're still against\Nescaping with everyone, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.80,0:14:36.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But it's different now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.68,0:14:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'll help you escape with everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.81,0:14:45.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,That's not like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.65,0:14:48.19,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you think he's lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.32,0:14:49.94,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.40,0:14:53.70,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray is now going to help everyone escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.90,0:14:57.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And we also have information\Nto trick Mom from the inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:57.99,0:14:59.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's awesome!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.58,0:15:03.54,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.46,0:15:07.21,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You knew about everything\Nfor a long time, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.50,0:15:10.05,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It must have been painful.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.34,0:15:12.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Knowing and sending them off\Nwithout saying anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.17,0:15:14.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So many of them.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.81,0:15:21.72,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.14,0:15:26.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Were the experiments for the tracking devices\Ndone on someone's ear?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.98,0:15:32.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What happened to that child...\Nor rather, children?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.61,0:15:35.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't cause them\Nto be shipped out early, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:35.99,0:15:39.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't sacrifice someone\Nfor our sake, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.45,0:15:43.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Actually, never mind. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.95,0:15:46.46,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks to that,\Nwe can all escape together now.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.17,0:15:48.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.13,0:15:52.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,don't do something like that ever again.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.26,0:15:55.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.30,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're not alone anymore, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.01,0:16:03.68,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I swear. I'll never do it again.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:04.39,0:16:06.56,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's all escape from here together.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.06,0:16:12.69,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They're talking on their own again, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.07,0:16:16.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it, how long are they\Ngoing to be discussing things?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.78,0:16:19.20,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We need to go save Conny!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.37,0:16:21.24,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if there's a reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.58,0:16:22.49,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Like what?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.99,0:16:24.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.58,0:16:28.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not just about being dangerous\Nbecause we're dealing with bad people.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.87,0:16:31.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But something even more...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:36.80,0:16:38.76,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Emma sure was mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.22,0:16:40.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Ray.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.34,0:16:42.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I want to ask you something.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:43.26,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.72,0:16:47.27,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You said you did it\Nso that both of us don't get killed.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.69,0:16:49.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But are you actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.14,0:16:50.15,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.86,0:16:53.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have something to report.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.82,0:17:01.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Gilda and I decided to properly\Nobserve Mom once again.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.57,0:17:04.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom disappears right before\Neight o'clock every night.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.58,0:17:05.58,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Disappears?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.70,0:17:08.96,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. She's nowhere to be found in the House.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.62,0:17:11.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,This House has a secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.92,0:17:13.17,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,A secret room?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.42,0:17:14.38,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.50,0:17:15.42,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Located here.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.76,0:17:18.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Next to Mom's bedroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.17,0:17:23.14,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom's bedroom has the bathroom\Nand washroom next to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:23.14,0:17:27.81,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Past that, continuing beyond the wall\Nis Mom's office.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.23,0:17:30.31,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But this probably isn't a wall.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.40,0:17:37.44,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I noticed that every time Mom disappears,\Nshe always goes into her office or the washroom.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.44,0:17:43.53,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,So I measured the distance inside the room,\Nand the distance in the hallway.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.70,0:17:45.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Oh. That's what you were doing then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.99,0:17:46.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.95,0:17:47.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And the result?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.20,0:17:49.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,They didn't match.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.16,0:17:53.08,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There are about ten\Nof my footsteps' worth of space.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.50,0:17:56.59,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,One side is a wall,\Nand the other side is a bookshelf.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:57.00,0:17:59.84,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But I think there are\Nhidden doors on both sides.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.01,0:18:02.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And beyond that, there's a secret room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.97,0:18:04.60,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But what is that for?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.60,0:18:05.55,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Probably—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.55,0:18:06.97,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Scheduled check-ins.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.18,0:18:10.10,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Mom does scheduled check-ins\Nto the headquarters every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.23,0:18:11.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The room is likely for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.44,0:18:13.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Headquarters?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.40,0:18:17.36,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,The base that supplies babies\Nand sisters to this House.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.28,0:18:21.28,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Ray, did you know\Nthat there was a room here?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.28,0:18:23.61,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,No. Although I suspected the existence—
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.61,0:18:24.99,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to get in.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.24,0:18:28.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's a way to communicate with the outside,\Nand find Conny and the others' whereabouts.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.91,0:18:31.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We might be able to find some clues!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.25,0:18:33.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But could we get in there so easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.87,0:18:36.00,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's difficult, we have to do it!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.00,0:18:38.63,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Hold on. There's no merit in going that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:38.96,0:18:43.47,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Even if it's a communication method,\Nit's most likely only connected to headquarters.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:43.47,0:18:46.89,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And Mom doesn't know\Nwhere our siblings were sent.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.22,0:18:49.39,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's not even an issue of finding clues.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.64,0:18:52.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And if we're careless, our tracking devices\Ncould give away our position.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.98,0:18:55.52,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,We don't know\Nwhat kind of security that room has.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.60,0:18:56.86,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's too dangerous.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.86,0:18:57.90,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.90,0:19:01.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I'm saying that the risk\Noverwhelmingly outweighs the merit.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.90,0:19:04.11,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,You're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:04.11,0:19:08.91,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,For now, be careful of the Sister.\NDon't dig your grave with a foolish move.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.91,0:19:09.79,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.29,0:19:14.29,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I have Mom under control,\Nbut we're doomed if the Sister finds out.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.79,0:19:16.33,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Keep that in mind when you act.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.38,0:19:23.80,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Don, can you go ahead to prepare for dinner?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.80,0:19:26.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,- If someone doesn't go, Mom will—\N- I know.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.28,0:19:44.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Don, that way is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.82,0:19:50.78,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Do you really intend to go in?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.95,0:19:53.87,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,I can't stay calm like them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.33,0:19:58.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,And I want to know the real Mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.61,0:20:24.82,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,There's a hidden door behind here.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.99,0:20:34.83,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,How is this set up?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.92,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Is there even one here?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:49.93,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Damn it! I need to hurry and go save her\Nas soon as possible!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:50.47,0:20:51.85,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Maybe...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.85,0:20:57.23,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Look closely at the shapes.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:06.40,0:21:07.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.20,0:21:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,It's locked.
